> @mbien I've forgotten where we're at with this one? I just noticed the incorrect hint again in NB15 while working on update check. Still need fixing for NB16?

@neilcsmith-net yes this should be reverted since my "[hotfix](https://github.com/apache/netbeans/pull/4421/files)" made the situation worse unfortunately. Since the patch also added tests and a little bit of an update to the ARRAY_WRITE, READ_METHODS and WRITE_METHODS, I was wondering if we can do a partial revert like proposed here.

Completely ok with a full revert too of course - I was only asking for feedback.
